### Some examples of sqoop eval command ###

=>It allows users to execute user-defined queries against respective database servers and preview the result in the console

sqoop eval \
--connect jdbc:mysql://localhost/retail_db \
--username root \
--password cloudera \
--query "Select * from deparatments" 

sqoop eval \
--connect jdbc:mysql://localhost/retail_db \
--username root \
--password cloudera \
--query "Insert INTO departments VALUES(1 , "John" , 20000)" 


